OL,3,CSecondary school in lockdown as police
OL,4,Crespond to 'online threat'
OL,6,FA secondary school in Brecon has been
OL,7,Fplaced into lockdown as police respond
OL,8,Fto a threat made online.
OL,10,FThe lockdown was implemented at Brecon
OL,11,FHigh School on Monday (27 April) at
OL,12,Faround midday.
OL,14,FDyfed-Powys Police said this was a
OL,15,F"precaution" and the measure would be
OL,16,Flifted at the end of the school day.
OL,18,FIn a statement on Monday afternoon,
OL,19,Fthe force said: "Dyfed-Powys Police is
OL,20,Fdealing with an incident at Brecon
OL,21,FHigh School today.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
