PN,46902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777471867
OL,3,CSecondary school in lockdown as police
OL,4,Crespond to 'online threat'
OL,6,F"Officers are currently working with
OL,7,Fthe school following a threat that has
OL,8,Fbeen made online.
OL,10,F"As a precaution and to prioritise
OL,11,Feveryone's safety, the school
OL,12,Fimplemented a lockdown of its
OL,13,Fperimeter, which meant no one could
OL,14,Fenter or leave the school site this
OL,15,Fafternoon.
OL,17,F"The perimeter lockdown is due to be
OL,18,Flifted at the end of the school day,
OL,19,Fand officers will maintain a visible
OL,20,Fpresence while pupils leave the
OL,21,Fschool."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
