PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777471867
OL,3,CSecondary school in lockdown as police
OL,4,Crespond to 'online threat'
OL,6,FIn a statement posted on the school's
OL,7,FFacebook page, Brecon High School
OL,8,FHeadteacher, Rob Edwards, confirmed
OL,9,Fthe school's site was under a
OL,10,F"perimeter lockdown" and no one is
OL,11,Fallowed to leave or enter the school
OL,12,Fpremises, following advice from Dyfed-
OL,13,FPowys Police.
OL,15,FThe statement which was published just
OL,16,Fbefore 2pm reads: "I am writing to
OL,17,Fprovide a brief update following
OL,18,Fadvice received from Dyfed-Powys
OL,19,FPolice.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
