PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777471867
OL,3,CSecondary school in lockdown as police
OL,4,Crespond to 'online threat'
OL,6,F"The school remains in a perimeter
OL,7,Flockdown. This means that no one is
OL,8,Fable to enter or leave the school site
OL,9,Fat this time. The police have
OL,10,Fconfirmed that it is safe for pupils
OL,11,Fto remain indoors, and lessons are
OL,12,Fcontinuing as normal.
OL,14,F"Lunch arrangements will take place as
OL,15,Fnormal, with pupils supervised inside
OL,16,Fand on site.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
