PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777471867
OL,3,CSecondary school in lockdown as police
OL,4,Crespond to 'online threat'
OL,6,F"We kindly ask that parents and carers
OL,7,Fdo not come to school to collect
OL,8,Fchildren at this time, as this may
OL,9,Fhinder the safe and effective
OL,10,Fmanagement of the situation.
OL,12,F"We will provide further updates as
OL,13,Fsoon as additional information is
OL,14,Favailable.
OL,16,F"Thank you for your continued
OL,17,Funderstanding and cooperation."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
